sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant JoinPage as /join/[campaignId] (Public)
  participant Login as /login (LoginForm)
  participant FirebaseAuth as Firebase Auth
  participant Email as User email
  participant Callback as /auth/callback
  participant API as POST /api/session
  participant Cookie as Session Cookie
  participant Action as joinCampaign() Server Action
  participant Firestore as Firestore

  Note over User,JoinPage: --- Campaign invite flow ---
  User->>JoinPage: Click DM's invite link
  JoinPage->>JoinPage: Validate token vs campaign.inviteToken
  JoinPage->>User: Show "Sign in to join [Campaign]"
  User->>JoinPage: Click "Sign in to join"
  JoinPage->>JoinPage: Store joinCampaignId + joinToken in sessionStorage
  JoinPage->>Login: redirect(/login)

  Note over User,Callback: --- Magic link auth ---
  User->>Login: Enter email
  Login->>FirebaseAuth: sendSignInLinkToEmail(email, callbackUrl)
  FirebaseAuth->>Email: Send magic link
  Login->>User: "Check your email"
  User->>Email: Click link
  Email->>Callback: GET /auth/callback?...
  Callback->>FirebaseAuth: signInWithEmailLink(email, url)
  FirebaseAuth-->>Callback: credential (idToken)
  Callback->>API: POST { idToken }
  API->>API: adminAuth().createSessionCookie(idToken)
  API->>Cookie: Set session cookie (httpOnly, 5 days)
  API-->>Callback: { ok: true }

  Note over Callback,Action: --- Post-login routing ---
  alt Pending join in sessionStorage
    Callback->>Callback: Read joinCampaignId + joinToken, clear sessionStorage
    Callback->>JoinPage: redirect(/join/[campaignId]?token=...)
    JoinPage->>User: Show "Join campaign" button (user now logged in)
    User->>Action: Submit join form
    Action->>Firestore: Create players doc (playerUserId = uid)
    Action->>Firestore: campaign.playerUserIds = arrayUnion(uid)
    Action->>User: redirect(/player/dashboard)
  else No pending join — DM account
    Callback->>User: redirect(/app/dashboard)
  end

  Note over User,Firestore: --- Player-only account ---
  Note right of Firestore: /app/dashboard checks:<br/>no owned campaigns + has player records<br/>→ redirect(/player/dashboard)
